            <lg xml:id="TK751">
<l>poruḷal lavaraip poruḷākac ceyyum</l>
<l>poruḷalla tillai poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Besides wealth there is nothing that can change people of no importance into those of (some) importance.</l>
            </lg>
